  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1  \u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bb1\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0baa \u0bae\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A laborer who went to collect firewood fell down and died tragically",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 60-year-old man who was going to collect firewood in Pallagewaduwa Indgala Estate (Division No. 6) fell and died in the tea garden.",
        "Today (06) around 09.30 in the morning, 60-year-old Duraisamy Chelladurai went to collect firewood in Pallagewaduwa Indgala plantation (Division No. 6), the plantation manager and the assistant manager visited the said area.",
        "The women workers who were gathering firewood in the area said that the person who had gone to collect firewood fell and died on the tea hill while returning home due to the fear of the plantation management."
      ],
